description: iZafe Group AB engages in the research, development, and marketing of medical products for safe, qualitative medication and drug management. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 9 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2011-04-04. Its offering includes Dosell, a patented drug dispenser under development that can be used when medicating patients at home via remote monitoring; and MediKoll, an app that provides patients information about side effects, reactions and allergies linked to different types of medication. The firm operates in the pharmaceutical industry, hospitals and care homes, and Pharmacies and private healthcare markets. The company is active globally.
naics: Navigational, Measuring, Electromedical, and Control Instruments Manufacturing
